{"tid":2091596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方致函：嚴辭批評傳媒不專業","createTime":"2020-07-02T18:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T18:38:42.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"253c2bdf1a16755b3b623c906436d6aa4f5578c6","tid":2091596,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T18:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方致函4個傳媒協會，反映7月1日銅鑼灣及灣仔一帶執法期間，發生3宗傳媒不專業行為，對此表示非常遺憾。警方向香港記者協會、攝影記者協會、新聞行政人員協會，及新聞工作者聯會發信，提到警方在百德新街近怡和街示威現場，發現一名身穿黃色、寫上「記者」字樣背心的女子，當時沒有進行採訪工作，其後確認她並非記者。這名女子之後涉嫌非法集結被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方又指，有警員於高士威道近興發街制服一名涉嫌參與非法集結的疑犯期間，被多人包圍襲擊、被利器插傷，大量出血，有網媒美化搶犯和襲警，認為該網媒的報道顛倒是非，令人不齒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，時代廣場有人將大量印有警員個人資料的單張撒在地上，有網媒特寫鏡頭，近距離拍攝及直播警員資料，做法極不專業，亦可能違反有關禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535497-20200703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535497-20200703.htm&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBPrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=db1b668a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535497-20200703.htm&h=11f38193\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535497-20200703.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五毛開始進場恐嚇，各位巴絲打可唔可以幫忙入嚟留個言</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxbFFY9CPduw&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBPrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=e87b7eb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw</a>"},{"pid":"c97309469461c479ac02e77510fedff1f693349b","tid":2091596,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfe13763eee0e14bf2f7580a2e6807cc715e46f","tid":